============
INTRODUCTION
============
bash greptools are some convenience functions build on top of grep.

============
INSTALLATION
============
To install bash greptools, copy the file 'bash_greptools' to your home directory, and then add the following line to your .bashrc file:

if [ -f ~/bash_greptools ]; then . ~/bash_greptools; fi

